We came with my MIL who was visiting us for lunch. The food we had was very tasty.

It included:
- veg spring rolls
- tandoori momos
- green Thai curry
- tandoori dal fry
- paneer makani
- paneer tacos
- cheesecake ice cream

The service was overall quite good. The momos were super spicy for my husband and MIL so they were kind enough to take the remaining back and adjust the sauce.

Only it took a really long time for them to send out my husband‚Äôs drink which was basically a thumbs up float with vanilla ice cream and we had to remind them at least 3 times. My MIL and I had mocktails that were more complicated to make and they came out right away.

They played good music, mostly covers of popular songs. We had a good laugh hearing Linkin Park‚Äôs ‚ÄúNumb‚Äù being played to a dance beat.

The seating is fun and creative, with an outdoor section with a swing bench.

### The Kitchen On Top: A Culinary Gem in Goa

Nestled atop a scenic vantage point in Goa, **The Kitchen On Top** shines with an impressive rating of **4.4**, bolstered by nearly **1,790 reviews** from patrons who have savored its delights. This charming eatery boasts a vibrant menu that caters to diverse palates, highlighted by specialties such as **momos** (56 mentions) and **tandoori** dishes (39 mentions). With its fusion of **North Indian food** and delectable **non-vegetarian** options, it's no surprise that guests emerge raving about their experiences.

### Ambiance & Design

The ambiance at The Kitchen On Top sets a perfect backdrop for any dining experience. Reviews frequently mention the **outdoor seating**, complete with a whimsical **swing** that enhances the restaurant's charm while offering breathtaking views of the surrounding mountains. The lighting is both warm and inviting, creating a casual yet upscale atmosphere perfect for celebrations or a cozy dinner for two. Patrons have been captivated by the restaurant's **transparent private dining spaces**, adding a unique twist to intimate gatherings. The sounds of soft music‚Äîoften lively covers of popular songs‚Äîdrift through the air, providing a pleasing auditory experience that enhances the overall vibe.

![Outdoor Seating at The Kitchen On Top](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkLj1tj8mgb4bESG6jEp-lUUzXYNTb5yERR8q1p5hnxvK7zrLqWvN2N1ObvaAJ7QAS2EWULeOltcSN7GeWHsyasaFS67UOTG6BELs_zELBOuU6zeqUiOwG9fxLwAGX_XrPKcgY=w375-h563-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at The Kitchen On Top features a delightful array of dishes that reflect a fusion of flavors and cultures. Signature items include the **pulled chicken Korean bao**, which has garnered rave reviews for its exquisite taste and stunning presentation. Other highlights noted by guests include the **five-spiced vegetables** dish‚Äîa vibrant mix of flavors and textures‚Äîand the **tandoori momos**, which some found exhilaratingly spicy but utterly delicious. 

For dessert, diners recommend the **brownie with ice cream**, served in generous portions, ensuring that your sweet tooth is thoroughly satisfied. A variety of dietary options cater to all preference, including vegetarian and vegan selections like **paneer makhani** and **green Thai curry**. 

![Delicious Spread at The Kitchen On Top](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnrXDjXYATvS5h1ZSDOh199kP7aOZ-1KsyFOxZoeuxzuFcmK24TSKdafbxxr_1g3H4hgqgc6Fy0k5Pft_857yufBe9pZpHA3PmPZa6Hw7u8lciIMsKMUh7wa3BsWrOeLax7qg=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Customer feedback emphasizes the attentive and friendly service at The Kitchen On Top. Staff members have received high marks for their willingness to provide recommendations, ensuring diners find dishes that perfectly suit their tastes. Although a few reviews mentioned delays‚Äîparticularly with drinks‚Äîthe overall sentiment leans positively, with most guests expressing satisfaction with the service speed and staff demeanor.

### Popularity & Reviews

The Kitchen On Top has thrived as a beloved spot among locals and tourists alike, earning itself a reputation for quality food and a lively atmosphere. Social media buzz showcases numerous guests sharing their experiences, contributing to the restaurant's high standing and returning clientele. The ambiance, food, and attentive service have led patrons to leave consistently positive sentiments; many note their eagerness to return and explore more of the menu.

![Stunning Plate Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdl8SVmORl8CHh9bQYCU0FBWpD5iLFS_rIa0oIUZsycgqhttnw99IJYT8sqzW2TAPWXINvfW1r7zXIN0cofLN9SbGOO8q8PHtQ3ngSBAYAXBGb8IPy5EXXTK-mpT14kfkGA05rqT=w375-h281-p)

### Conclusion

In conclusion, The Kitchen On Top is more than just a restaurant; it‚Äôs an experience filled with flavor, scenic beauty, and great company. Whether you're celebrating a special moment or simply looking to enjoy a meal with a view, this culinary destination in Goa is sure to tantalize your taste buds and leave lasting memories. With a commitment to quality and an atmosphere that invites you to linger a little longer, this restaurant deserves its spot on every food lover's itinerary.
